());\n        }\n\n        private RecordingObjectOutputStream(ByteArrayOutputStream output) throws IOException {\n            super(output);\n            this.output = output;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public void defaultWriteObject() {\n        }\n\n        private byte[] serializedObject() throws IOException {\n            flush();\n            return output.toByteArray();\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static final class ReplayingObjectInputStream extends ObjectInputStream {\n        private ReplayingObjectInputStream(byte[] serializedObject) throws IOException {\n            super(new ByteArrayInputStream(serializedObject));\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public void defaultReadObject() {\n        }\n    }\n"}]}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 3552, "output": 2727, "cacheRead": 27648, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 33927, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1778110729552, "responseId": "resp_0582509a8448333a0169fbd10a34ec81a1b71fecc7563a7175"}}
